## 🗄️ Database Schema

### Table Count: **9 tables** + **1 view**

| # | Table | Purpose |
|---|-------|---------|
| 1 | `employers` | Companies posting jobs |
| 2 | `categories` | Job categories (Accounting, IT, Healthcare, etc.) |
| 3 | `locations` | Cities & counties (Nairobi, Mombasa, etc.) |
| 4 | `jobs` | Core job listings |
| 5 | `sponsored_ads` | Paid promotions (time-based) |
| 6 | `opportunities_hub` | Bursaries, scholarships, internships, university admissions, sponsorships, certifications |
| 7 | `blogs` | Content marketing & SEO articles |
| 8 | `job_applications` | Track applicants per job |
| 9 | `sitemap_urls` | **VIEW** – auto-generates sitemap.xml |

---

### 🔹 Table: `employers`

```sql
CREATE TABLE employers (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    slug VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    phone VARCHAR(20),
    logo_url VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    website VARCHAR(255),
    is_trusted BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    
    INDEX idx_slug (slug),
    INDEX idx_trusted (is_trusted)
);
```

---

### 🔹 Table: `categories`

```sql
CREATE TABLE categories (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    slug VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    meta_title VARCHAR(150),
    meta_description VARCHAR(320),
    icon VARCHAR(50),
    display_order INT DEFAULT 0,
    is_popular BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    
    INDEX idx_slug (slug),
    INDEX idx_popular (is_popular),
    INDEX idx_display_order (display_order)
);
```

---

### 🔹 Table: `locations`

```sql
CREATE TABLE locations (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    city VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    slug VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    county VARCHAR(100),
    meta_title VARCHAR(150),
    meta_description VARCHAR(320),
    job_count INT DEFAULT 0,
    is_popular BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    
    INDEX idx_slug (slug),
    INDEX idx_popular (is_popular),
    INDEX idx_county (county)
);
```

