## 🔍 High-Traffic Page Queries

### 1. Entry Level Jobs – `/jobs/level/entry`

```sql
SELECT j.*, e.company_name, e.logo_url, l.city, c.name as category_name,
       CASE WHEN s.id IS NOT NULL AND s.start_date <= CURDATE() AND s.end_date >= CURDATE() 
            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as is_sponsored
FROM jobs j
JOIN employers e ON j.employer_id = e.id
LEFT JOIN locations l ON j.location_id = l.id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON j.category_id = c.id
LEFT JOIN sponsored_ads s ON j.id = s.job_id AND s.start_date <= CURDATE() AND s.end_date >= CURDATE() AND s.payment_status = 'paid'
WHERE j.experience_level = 'entry'
  AND j.is_active = TRUE
  AND j.application_deadline >= CURDATE()
ORDER BY is_sponsored DESC, j.created_at DESC
LIMIT 25 OFFSET 0;
```

---

### 2. County Government Jobs – `/county/kiambu`

```sql
SELECT j.*, e.company_name, c.name as category_name
FROM jobs j
JOIN employers e ON j.employer_id = e.id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON j.category_id = c.id
WHERE j.government_level = 'county'
  AND j.county_name = 'Kiambu'
  AND j.is_active = TRUE
  AND j.application_deadline >= CURDATE()
ORDER BY j.created_at DESC;
```

---

### 3. Bursaries – `/opportunities/bursaries`

```sql
SELECT * FROM opportunities_hub
WHERE opportunity_type = 'bursary'
  AND is_active = TRUE
  AND deadline >= CURDATE()
ORDER BY 
  CASE WHEN deadline <= DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 14 DAY) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END,
  created_at DESC;
```

